OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772625779
OL,3,CFormer police officer admits sexual
OL,4,Cassault and misconduct
OL,6,FA former West Yorkshire police officer
OL,7,Fis facing jail after he admitted
OL,8,Finappropriately trying to befriend two
OL,9,Fwomen and sexually assaulting one of
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,FPatrick Banks, 42, had inappropriate
OL,13,Fmessage exchanges with the women and
OL,14,Fasked one of them to translate a
OL,15,Fmessage saying, "I want to take your
OL,16,Funderwear off with my teeth", a court
OL,17,Fheard.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
