PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772625779
OL,3,CFormer police officer admits sexual
OL,4,Cassault and misconduct
OL,6,FThe offences happened both on and off
OL,7,Fduty when he was working as a
OL,8,Fdetective constable in Leeds, West
OL,9,FYorkshire Police have said.
OL,11,FBanks appeared at Sheffield Crown
OL,12,FCourt on Monday where he pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to two counts of misconduct in
OL,14,Fa public office and one count of
OL,15,Fsexual assault, involving touching one
OL,16,Fof the women.
OL,18,FHe denied one charge of stealing a
OL,19,Fmobile phone.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
