FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772625779
OL,3,CFormer police officer admits sexual
OL,4,Cassault and misconduct
OL,6,FJudge Jeremy Richardson KC, the
OL,7,FRecorder of Sheffield, said that
OL,8,Fcharge would lie on file.
OL,10,FThe court heard that Banks "wilfully
OL,11,Fengaged in inappropriate messaging"
OL,12,Fover five months in 2024 and 2025 with
OL,13,Fthe first woman, and met up with her.
OL,15,FHe is also accused of lying about
OL,16,Fbeing a rabbi to gain her trust, but
OL,17,Fthe court heard he denies this.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
