PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772625779
OL,3,CFormer police officer admits sexual
OL,4,Cassault and misconduct
OL,6,FA judge heard he engaged in
OL,7,Finappropriate messages outside
OL,8,Fprofessional communication with the
OL,9,Fsecond woman over a month last year,
OL,10,Fbought gifts for her child and
OL,11,Fattended her address as a police
OL,12,Fofficer.
OL,14,FHe invited her to translate messages
OL,15,Ffrom French to English which said, "I
OL,16,Fwant to take your underwear off with
OL,17,Fmy teeth", the court was told.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
