PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772625779
OL,3,CFormer police officer admits sexual
OL,4,Cassault and misconduct
OL,6,FThe judge heard that Banks tried to
OL,7,Fbefriend both women and attended their
OL,8,Fhomes, in one case it was while he was
OL,9,Foff duty and in the other case, three
OL,10,Fout of four times were off duty.
OL,12,FBanks will be sentenced on April 1 and
OL,13,Fwas bailed until then.
OL,15,FJudge Richardson said: "It is always a
OL,16,Fvery serious matter for a police
OL,17,Fofficer to misconduct himself.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
