FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1772625779
OL,3,CFormer police officer admits sexual
OL,4,Cassault and misconduct
OL,6,F"The sentence in such cases, I'm sure
OL,7,Fyou appreciate, is invariably an
OL,8,Fimmediate custodial sentence which
OL,9,Falways falls hard on an individual who
OL,10,Fhas, at least in part, been
OL,11,Fresponsible for upholding the law.
OL,13,F"The only issue really to be decided
OL,14,Fis how long that sentence needs to be."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
